[
    {
        "text": "This is the fourth Dragon King of Bhutan.",
        "startTime": 5,
        "endTime": 2675,
        "slowStartTime": 157,
        "slowEndTime": 4238
    },
    {
        "text": "A beautiful country at the eastern end of the Himalayas.",
        "startTime": 3347,
        "endTime": 6511,
        "slowStartTime": 5170,
        "slowEndTime": 9992
    },
    {
        "text": "He became king at the age of 17 in 1972.",
        "startTime": 7263,
        "endTime": 11318,
        "slowStartTime": 11044,
        "slowEndTime": 17202
    },
    {
        "text": "It was then, when he had to decide what should be the philosophy behind his reign.",
        "startTime": 11884,
        "endTime": 16691,
        "slowStartTime": 17976,
        "slowEndTime": 25262
    },
    {
        "text": "He looked at other countries and noticed in most of them,...",
        "startTime": 17944,
        "endTime": 21265,
        "slowStartTime": 27066,
        "slowEndTime": 32122
    },
    {
        "text": "...the government and the people strive for economical wealth.",
        "startTime": 21508,
        "endTime": 24919,
        "slowStartTime": 32412,
        "slowEndTime": 37603
    },
    {
        "text": "And those few who achieve this goal usually live a comfortable life,...",
        "startTime": 25821,
        "endTime": 30683,
        "slowStartTime": 38881,
        "slowEndTime": 46250
    },
    {
        "text": "...but on the downside many other people live in misery, poverty or social isolation.",
        "startTime": 31011,
        "endTime": 37701,
        "slowStartTime": 46666,
        "slowEndTime": 56776
    },
    {
        "text": "Also in the ruthless hunt for money, huge parts of the environment are often destroyed.",
        "startTime": 38695,
        "endTime": 44605,
        "slowStartTime": 58192,
        "slowEndTime": 67132
    },
    {
        "text": "This couldn't be the right path for Bhutan.",
        "startTime": 45522,
        "endTime": 47843,
        "slowStartTime": 68433,
        "slowEndTime": 71990
    },
    {
        "text": "The concept of Gross National Happiness was born.",
        "startTime": 48530,
        "endTime": 51640,
        "slowStartTime": 72945,
        "slowEndTime": 77685
    },
    {
        "text": "The primary idea of GNH is that every human being aspires for happiness...",
        "startTime": 52363,
        "endTime": 58185,
        "slowStartTime": 78694,
        "slowEndTime": 87503
    },
    {
        "text": "...and the country's development should also be measured in its citizen's happiness.",
        "startTime": 58877,
        "endTime": 63219,
        "slowStartTime": 88465,
        "slowEndTime": 95054
    },
    {
        "text": "The fourth Dragon King's challenge, therefore, was figuring out how to balance economic development...",
        "startTime": 64253,
        "endTime": 70317,
        "slowStartTime": 96530,
        "slowEndTime": 105701
    },
    {
        "text": "...with the emotional and spiritual well-being of his people.",
        "startTime": 70780,
        "endTime": 74141,
        "slowStartTime": 106320,
        "slowEndTime": 111436
    },
    {
        "text": "Although economical growth can't be the only goal,...",
        "startTime": 75610,
        "endTime": 78815,
        "slowStartTime": 113565,
        "slowEndTime": 118447
    },
    {
        "text": "...a flourishing economy gives the government the funds needed...",
        "startTime": 79460,
        "endTime": 82742,
        "slowStartTime": 119340,
        "slowEndTime": 124338
    },
    {
        "text": "...to provide a working health and educational system...",
        "startTime": 82851,
        "endTime": 85753,
        "slowStartTime": 124427,
        "slowEndTime": 128854
    },
    {
        "text": "...as well as certain living standards.",
        "startTime": 86156,
        "endTime": 87883,
        "slowStartTime": 129384,
        "slowEndTime": 132050
    },
    {
        "text": "Because being healthy, having opportunities for the future...",
        "startTime": 89579,
        "endTime": 93223,
        "slowStartTime": 134519,
        "slowEndTime": 140059
    },
    {
        "text": "...and knowing that security, a steady income, housing...",
        "startTime": 93569,
        "endTime": 97423,
        "slowStartTime": 140504,
        "slowEndTime": 146359
    },
    {
        "text": "...or well-balanced time use are guaranteed is crucial for people to be happy.",
        "startTime": 97701,
        "endTime": 102745,
        "slowStartTime": 146702,
        "slowEndTime": 154342
    },
    {
        "text": "But furthermore, people get a lot of positive energy from being with others...",
        "startTime": 103731,
        "endTime": 108576,
        "slowStartTime": 155746,
        "slowEndTime": 163089
    },
    {
        "text": "...and sharing interests.",
        "startTime": 108812,
        "endTime": 110002,
        "slowStartTime": 163368,
        "slowEndTime": 165228
    },
    {
        "text": "Participating in cultural life and to hold up local traditions and cultural heritage...",
        "startTime": 110757,
        "endTime": 116511,
        "slowStartTime": 166285,
        "slowEndTime": 174992
    },
    {
        "text": "...lead to a stronger community feeling.",
        "startTime": 116820,
        "endTime": 118897,
        "slowStartTime": 175380,
        "slowEndTime": 178570
    },
    {
        "text": "Healthy family relationships, advocating community activities and religious aspects...",
        "startTime": 119755,
        "endTime": 125564,
        "slowStartTime": 179783,
        "slowEndTime": 188571
    },
    {
        "text": "...are factors for achieving happiness.",
        "startTime": 125841,
        "endTime": 128063,
        "slowStartTime": 188912,
        "slowEndTime": 192319
    },
    {
        "text": "It gives the Bhutanese people a strong sense of values and identity.",
        "startTime": 129089,
        "endTime": 133784,
        "slowStartTime": 193784,
        "slowEndTime": 200901
    },
    {
        "text": "The fourth Dragon King reigned 34 years...",
        "startTime": 135232,
        "endTime": 138666,
        "slowStartTime": 202998,
        "slowEndTime": 208224
    },
    {
        "text": "...basing his decisions on all factors of Gross National Happiness...",
        "startTime": 138868,
        "endTime": 142925,
        "slowStartTime": 208452,
        "slowEndTime": 214612
    },
    {
        "text": "...asking himself, \"What makes Buthan's people happy?\"",
        "startTime": 143356,
        "endTime": 147427,
        "slowStartTime": 215184,
        "slowEndTime": 221365
    },
    {
        "text": "And the fourth Dragon King lived by example, leading a very simple life.",
        "startTime": 148026,
        "endTime": 152904,
        "slowStartTime": 222189,
        "slowEndTime": 229581
    },
    {
        "text": "In fact, he believed so strongly in the concept of GNH...",
        "startTime": 153477,
        "endTime": 158235,
        "slowStartTime": 230365,
        "slowEndTime": 237578
    },
    {
        "text": "...that he even decided to hand over sovereignty to the people.",
        "startTime": 158697,
        "endTime": 161965,
        "slowStartTime": 238196,
        "slowEndTime": 243172
    },
    {
        "text": "In 2006, he retired as king at the age of 52 and changed the course of history.",
        "startTime": 162778,
        "endTime": 170157,
        "slowStartTime": 244317,
        "slowEndTime": 255460
    },
    {
        "text": "Two years later, in 2008, Bhutan elected its first representative parliament.",
        "startTime": 170823,
        "endTime": 176707,
        "slowStartTime": 256385,
        "slowEndTime": 265285
    },
    {
        "text": "Since then, the idea of Gross National Happiness...",
        "startTime": 177343,
        "endTime": 181390,
        "slowStartTime": 266165,
        "slowEndTime": 272310
    },
    {
        "text": "...has taken quite some momentum outside of Bhutan...",
        "startTime": 181741,
        "endTime": 185026,
        "slowStartTime": 272762,
        "slowEndTime": 277764
    },
    {
        "text": "...with other countries and people around the world...",
        "startTime": 185420,
        "endTime": 188315,
        "slowStartTime": 278280,
        "slowEndTime": 282698
    },
    {
        "text": "...thinking about adopting the GNH approach to strive for development with values...",
        "startTime": 188687,
        "endTime": 194484,
        "slowStartTime": 283180,
        "slowEndTime": 291951
    },
    {
        "text": "...and to make the world a happier place.",
        "startTime": 194833,
        "endTime": 197470,
        "slowStartTime": 292400,
        "slowEndTime": 296430
    }
]